==English==

===Etymology===
From [[in-]] + [[flex]] + [[-ible]]

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-inflexible.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Adjective===
'''inflexible'''

# Not [[flexible]]; not capable of [[bend]]ing or being bent; [[stiff]]; [[rigid]]; [[firm]]; [[unyielding]].
# Not willing to [[change]], e.g. one's [[opinion]] or [[habits]]; [[obstinate]]; [[resolute]]; [[determined]].

====Related terms====
*[[inflexibility]]
*[[inflexibleness]]
*[[inflexibly]]

